{
  "text": "Can you tell me if we have covered the necessary material to this point to, if published, make the necessary reparations for the naïve actions? I am Ra. We mean no disrespect for your service, but we do not expect to make full reparations for these distortions. We may, however, offer our thoughts in the attempt. The attempt is far more important to us than the completeness of the result. The nature of your language is such that what is distorted cannot, to our knowledge, be fully undistorted but only illuminated somewhat.",
